{"tid":1225111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今鋪新仇舊恨一次過同佢地算清！！","createTime":"2019-06-15T06:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T04:27:50.000Z","uid":120623,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd62bc2bcb42521904d4979ec9076d653d11f74","tid":1225111,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:33:37.000Z","msg":"616大命題依然係反送中，一日唔徹一日都唔可以罷休！！！<br />\n<br />\n中間開槍狂掟催淚同噴椒、中彈爆眼爆血瀕死既義士、黑警打手無寸鐵既人、呀伯後生仔女都被一棍棍毆落去、全城搜捕，因為69、612被拘捕既人，甚至再之前已經因爲反送中被拉既人.......<br />\n<br />\n呢啲我地可以當冇發生過咩？？？？？<br />\n<br />\n前前後後佔中同大小社運被拉既人，黃之鋒梁天琦等等等等，立法會DQ，甚至係呢三十年內發生過既所有黑暗野，我地一炮過同佢計！！！<br />\n<br />\n仲未提即使徹完逃犯，仲有國歌法人工島黎緊！<br />\n<br />\n未完咖！<br />\n616要出黎！<br />\n叫多啲人出黎！<br />\n<br />\n之後都要繼續出！<br />\n即使係發展到每個禮拜野餐都要出！<br />\n一日未算清一日都唔可以退！！！"},{"pid":"4521909db2659f3c8c7853401190944447fc9ca2","tid":1225111,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601dd2a39ab19f0ae3bee165a4601e208be3e447","tid":1225111,"uid":83052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"好多人係IG見到暫緩就鬆懈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以多啲人提出，暫緩唔係撤回，共軍用嘅招「敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追」<br />\n群眾一退就危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8a3d4c48e73079815e585572e7d69520709a2b","tid":1225111,"uid":120623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"601dd2a39ab19f0ae3bee165a4601e208be3e447","tid":1225111,"uid":83052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"好多人係IG見到暫緩就鬆懈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i